Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是博克岛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.54,0:01:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的神秘感可谓是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举世无双
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  可能看起来并不起眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这潮湿的岩石群中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却藏着不少惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的生活精彩绝伦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.56,0:01:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是不适合胆小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道  其他地方的人都喜欢削削木头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者绣绣花什么的  而我们博克岛人则喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一种小小的娱乐活动  名为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛龙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啦  小鱼脚  你是想要这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻涕唠  那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝  给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有说过你今天看上去很美吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你真的很美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  喷喷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭味都传到我这儿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃吧  她还是讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让这里燃起来吧  吐吐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双胞胎得九分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丝翠得三分紧随其后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鱼脚和鼻涕唠各得零分垫底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不见踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的促膝谈心是不是吓到他了  史推克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么  鼻涕唠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我的女神  她有求  我必应
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:03:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴芙奈  她不是想把你活埋来着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就埋了几个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看他们  冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙曾是这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头号公敌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那都是五年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他们都在岛上定居了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的  他们有什么理由不搬来这呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有定制的龙舍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全天供应的自助餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全方位的龙浴服务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至还有最先进的火灾应对措施
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么自夸请别见怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候了  戈伯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  最后一轮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是黑羊  上吧  风中飞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有机会赢得比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-来吧  喷喷  -我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊  肉球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快飞  快飞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该你上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你旅途愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往上  往上  往上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好  肉球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你  亲爱的  我的这个值十分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  黑羊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个在争暴芙奈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我赢定了  -是我们俩一起赢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我现在无人可挡了  -除了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是连在一起的  蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想把我的荣耀偷走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-搞定他们  艾丝翠  -是我的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-成事不足败事有余  -没羊就没荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丝翠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我未来的儿媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风中飞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一共十三分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丝翠赢得了比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  博克岛堪称完美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最终得偿所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这也是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维京人能驭龙翱翔之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界也变得辽阔了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想再试一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没牙仔  不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这感觉太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没牙仔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚真是始料未及
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得再训练下你的单独滑行  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个固定尾翼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不方便进行救援行动  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们又找到一处  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  你想要我道歉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为这个在生闷气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感受到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感受到我真诚的歉意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  得了  别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会想残害一个独腿的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是对的  你是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你赢了  你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一场恶斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙和维京人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战况愈演愈烈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道口水洗不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们给这里取什么名字好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就叫痒胳肢窝岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许能在树林里找到几只割木龙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者在岩石群里找到些致命耳语龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢  或许我们最终能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二只夜煞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真是大发现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午好  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你去哪了  -你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了几场比赛  不然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正该问的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-躲我爸爸  -不是吧  又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定爱听这段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一早醒来  阳光明媚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屋顶上有几只
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖龙在唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我优哉游哉地下楼吃早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着世界上一切安好  结果我听到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿子  我们得谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不行  爸爸  我一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都得忙着去瞎转悠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  首先
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说话声音才不那样  你到底在模仿谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会那样耸肩膀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也太夸张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,言归正传啊  他说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是博克岛的骄傲  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我也以你为荣  -谢谢  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得自己很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么时候变得这么爱挥手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚还那么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  你就...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很严肃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也长大成人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你已经证明了自己能够委以重任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我决定...  -让你当部落首领  老天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嗝嗝  这太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,频繁使用弹簧圈会磨损
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很难校准的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在头疼的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么答复他的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没答复他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他转过身来  我已经跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  你已经身负重任了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画地图的事肯定得暂时搁置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果以后你没有时间的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得由我来飞没牙仔  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法胜任  艾丝翠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些演讲啊  规划啊  还有管理村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是他的长项
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没理解重点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说  当首领
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换我肯定激动死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直知道自己想要的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都是  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在找寻自己的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道自己不会像父亲那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没见过我母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我究竟该成为怎样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要找寻的并不在远方  小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许只是你还没认识到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远方好像有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  放松  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-发射  -艾丝翠  小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把腿绑住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那不会是真的吧  -住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风中飞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的老天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是一只夜煞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为他们都绝迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们交上好运了  伙计们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德拉戈的龙族大军里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定还没有夜煞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙族大军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  我们不想惹麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在偷走我们所有的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且摧毁我们的堡垒之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就该想到这点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没错  -对  你瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得这是我们干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕龙这活儿本身已经够困难了  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还遇上个行侠仗义的龙骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-偷偷摸摸地救龙捣乱  -什么行侠仗义的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有别的龙骑士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了你那个盗龙的朋友吗  你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也许有只能喷冰的龙给你撑腰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们必须得完成我们的捕龙指标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我们怎么跟德拉戈·布达威斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解释这烂摊子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德拉戈什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的这些都是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正等着明天我们为他的龙族大军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扩充一群新成员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德拉戈不喜欢听借口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上回空手回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就给了我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说以后就不会这么手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  听着  我们没听过什么盗龙贼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么喷冰龙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者你那个疯子老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有他的龙族大军  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把我们的龙还回来  我们就离开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从没见过这么凶巴巴的怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的礼貌都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫艾瑞特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我父亲同名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世上最好的捕龙猎手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜煞不是人人都能抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫没牙仔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说我们现在就离开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上  伙计们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风中飞  快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤  撤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些龙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是留不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德拉戈会把它们全部抢走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  肉球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你好  史推克  -你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  嫉妒唠  比赛真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  艾克夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有他的消息吗  -他现在可能已经
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞得无影无踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定想让那娃管理村庄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有机会延迟退休
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他准备好了  你会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博克岛的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总算决定回来工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  耽搁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  能跟你聊两句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事等不及要告诉我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你想的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  确实有事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一课  首领第一要务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是服务于人民
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  四十一号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能不能找个人少的地方聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-四十...  -是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我排在你前面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能不能谈...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  我都在这儿等一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要一个高龙鞍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打满铁钉的那种  还要带一个大储物箱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没问题  保证给你  -爸爸  我要说的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比造龙鞍更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二课  为人民服务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论大事小事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-可是  爸爸  -抱歉  葛伦普
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们能不能谈谈  -葛伦普
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又让锻炉熄灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够了  葛伦普  你就等着被别人领养吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好的  -给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-爸爸  -动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的  我必须
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我们发现新大陆的事告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-新大陆  -有新品种的龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没能仔细探索
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人不太友好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的夜煞还有致命纳得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.36,0:18:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没让他们乐翻天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有往常的兴高采烈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和让我陶醉的欢呼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人都是猎手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕龙猎手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该看看他们的堡垒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全炸裂开  卡在巨大的冰锥里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去无比怪异
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次见那样的场面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最糟糕的是  他们以为是我们干的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会给自己惹上大麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是所有人都喜欢这种生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈伯说得没错  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最好待在自己家乡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  你还有更重要的事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只等我来宣布这个重磅消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在组建龙族大军
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说他们的老板在组建龙族大军
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫什么德拉戈·被打威斯之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是他妄想抢走我的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就用我的脸血染他的拳头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴美女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布达威斯  德拉戈·布达威斯是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-所有龙停飞  -什么  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关上大门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-降下外门  -等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么回事  -快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听命令  锁门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有龙和维京人不准离开本岛半步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  就因为你认识的某人在遥远的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆地制造麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为德拉戈·布达威斯是个疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无道德和同情心可言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是他组建了龙族大军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最好早做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-把它们送回笼子  -是  史推克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就飞回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着那些捕龙猎手找到德拉戈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劝他理智些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我们要在岛上建防御工事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维护和平是我们的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平结束了  小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们必须为战争做好准备  -战争
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  要是德拉戈来抢我们的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能坐以待毙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去找到他  劝他改变想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  有些人是劝不动的  小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要担心的是博克岛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首领要保卫自己的领土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护龙厩  全部上锁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-小嗝嗝  别去  -我没得选
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擦亮眼睛  伙计们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借着这阵风  我们天亮就能找到德拉戈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们最好把这艘船装满龙  要快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间挑剔了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾瑞特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我们不想脑袋搬家...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就抓紧时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在左舷船尾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,网住它们  伙计们  把它们打下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共有两只  在左上方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回你们逃不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装弹  装弹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快  装弹  有人入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稳住了  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我还在担心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会空手而归呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的  今天是你的幸运日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们投降
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有条夜煞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一条致命纳得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有两位技压群雄的神秘龙骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样老板就能满意了  是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.41,0:22:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.64,0:22:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没牙仔  别动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙其实不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狭窄的空间  所以它们跟你们待一起好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们不会惹麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.82,0:22:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你先挑事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汪洋大海上的一艘木帆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的游泳技术怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.83,0:22:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-囚犯不能携带武器  -把它给我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么计划
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为捕龙猎人准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边是涂着凶煞梦魇唾液的长剑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.11,0:23:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一边会喷射凶恶双头龙的瓦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.88,0:23:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需一点火花然后...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.81,0:23:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  就会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们一旦开始把你看作同类
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.85,0:23:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就连最暴躁的龙都可以驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.48,0:23:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那个给我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在玩什么把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是把戏  我们只是想见德拉戈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我要改变他关于龙的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.47,0:23:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他劝人很有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要赢得龙的忠心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他便会为你赴汤蹈火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你改变不了这里任何人的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我此时此地就可以改变你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.05,0:23:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-当心  -龙骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.13,0:23:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻涕唠  你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.60,0:24:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我把你保护得多好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.74,0:24:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些网是干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.12,0:24:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心  刚才真是...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.71,0:24:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.81,0:24:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天呐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.75,0:24:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.59,0:24:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.03,0:24:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止射击
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.07,0:24:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.00,0:24:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来解救你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.17,0:24:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要解救
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.94,0:24:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.81,0:24:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.18,0:24:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上错船了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.98,0:24:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是艾瑞特  和我父亲...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.82,0:24:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同名...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.25,0:24:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.96,0:24:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这家伙从我身上弄走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.16,0:24:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有谁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.83,0:25:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.70,0:25:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  备龙鞍
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.80,0:25:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回家
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.00,0:25:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.03,0:25:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直毫无责任心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.94,0:25:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要保护我们的龙  阻止一场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.91,0:25:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么能是不负责任呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.14,0:25:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为战争正是他想要的  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.75,0:25:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多年前  有过一场盛大的首领聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.72,0:25:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专门讨论我们当时面临的龙灾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.25,0:25:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我们中走出一位来自陌生大陆的陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.79,0:25:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑身布满伤疤  身披一顶龙皮斗篷
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.63,0:25:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不带武器
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.23,0:25:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,语气柔和
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.93,0:25:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说他叫
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.27,0:25:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德拉戈·布达威斯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.64,0:25:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一介平民
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.71,0:25:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,致力于从龙的奴役中解放人类
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.28,0:25:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他仅凭一己之力就可以控制龙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.75,0:25:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他独自一人就可以保证大家安全
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.12,0:25:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们臣服于他
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.25,0:26:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追随他
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.26,0:26:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-愚蠢至极  -真好笑  
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.63,0:26:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我们也笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.83,0:26:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到他裹紧斗篷
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.29,0:26:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高喊着
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.76,0:26:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就等着瞧没有我你们怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.63,0:26:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着瞧没有我你们能怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.26,0:26:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房顶瞬间燃起大火
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.20,0:26:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身披盔甲的龙从火中蹿出
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.01,0:26:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把大厅烧成了灰
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.14,0:26:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.98,0:26:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是唯一一个幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.25,0:26:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀人不找理由的人不会和你讲道理的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.19,0:26:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-也许吧  -小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.06,0:26:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我还是要试试
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.93,0:26:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我所擅长的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.80,0:26:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我能改变你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.80,0:26:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能改变他的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.90,0:26:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.34,0:26:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-出发  -不
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.68,0:26:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带其他人回博克岛去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.61,0:26:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一天已经够乱的了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.35,0:27:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喜欢这个
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.12,0:27:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴芙奈
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.89,0:27:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.31,0:27:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.98,0:27:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让任何人伤害到你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.95,0:27:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.19,0:27:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.96,0:27:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没完没了了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.67,0:27:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.40,0:27:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.73,0:28:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稳住  稳住
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.94,0:28:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没牙仔
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.09,0:29:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我的龙扔在那儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.86,0:29:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他自己不能飞  他会被淹死的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.79,0:29:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得调头去找我的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.90,0:30:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.01,0:30:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盗龙贼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.31,0:30:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德拉戈·布达威斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.58,0:30:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听得懂
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.48,0:30:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.49,0:31:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没牙仔
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.22,0:31:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了  没事了  没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.03,0:31:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高兴见到你  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.13,0:31:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真让我担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.18,0:31:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.98,0:32:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.65,0:32:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多年过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.99,0:32:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.49,0:32:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.13,0:32:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.46,0:32:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.63,0:32:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当时还是个婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.04,0:32:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但母亲绝不会忘记自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.68,0:32:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.35,0:32:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倔脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.18,0:32:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他母亲一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.52,0:32:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也从不肯老实待着
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.52,0:32:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才二十岁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.59,0:32:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是一个维京人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.16,0:32:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这俩因素恐怕是最糟的组合了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.86,0:32:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想你自己早年是有多么的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.13,0:32:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,固执和愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.56,0:32:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.27,0:32:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看其实现在也没变多少
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.60,0:32:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.24,0:33:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会放弃的  戈伯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.11,0:33:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且如果小嗝嗝在我们找到他之前
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.71,0:33:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就找到了德拉戈的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.05,0:33:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嗝嗝不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.58,0:33:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要那条夜煞跟在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.72,0:33:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是条夜煞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.55,0:33:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.74,0:33:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到他们  裂颅
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.14,0:33:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到他们
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.75,0:33:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.68,0:33:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这边  -回来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.09,0:33:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-来  -你不能
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.72,0:33:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说完那种话然后转身就走
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.02,0:33:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.49,0:33:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说  究竟怎么...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.09,0:33:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  你能理解这听起来有多疯狂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.13,0:33:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.36,0:33:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有话问你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.53,0:33:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么些年你到底
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.40,0:34:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.57,0:34:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.40,0:34:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们告诉我说你死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.34,0:34:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都以为你是被龙吃掉...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.15,0:34:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你二十年来待的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.59,0:34:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直致力于拯救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.76,0:35:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.63,0:35:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你不生气吗  -什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.36,0:35:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.17,0:35:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说老实话  我还没回过神来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.84,0:35:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点疯狂凶猛的义务龙骑士自称是我母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.71,0:35:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事毕竟不是每天都会遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.88,0:35:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我并不无趣  对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.45,0:35:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这点
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.22,0:35:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.32,0:35:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.16,0:35:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.23,0:35:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.49,0:35:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找不到合适的词来表达
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.40,0:35:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能摸摸他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.61,0:35:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真美
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.14,0:35:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊艳绝世
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.68,0:35:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很有可能就是他们种族的最后一只了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.88,0:35:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.35,0:35:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和你一样大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.29,0:36:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得你们这么合得来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.36,0:36:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的牙还可以收缩
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.90,0:36:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.20,0:36:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在树林里发现了他
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.73,0:36:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被打了下来  受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.94,0:36:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只比齿龙因为
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.68,0:36:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德拉戈·布达威斯的铁捕龙夹丢了一条腿
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.38,0:36:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只止雨龙的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.85,0:36:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被剃刀网划伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.22,0:36:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这只可怜的陆行龙
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.59,0:36:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一个树枝陷阱弄瞎了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.49,0:36:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在孤单害怕中被丢下等死
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.72,0:36:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.79,0:36:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是德拉戈和他的捕龙夹干的好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.33,0:36:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.83,0:36:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇葩的点在于
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.57,0:36:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他打下来的人其实是我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.51,0:36:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.28,0:36:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也报复我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.34,0:36:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.75,0:37:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能把我完整的救下来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.71,0:37:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非要跟我扯平不可
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.48,0:37:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才有了这假肢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.46,0:37:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲对你这夜煞朋友是什么看法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.96,0:37:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始他不怎么接受
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.30,0:37:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过后来  他改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.87,0:37:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.00,0:37:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.60,0:37:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家乡的人都有了自己的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.44,0:37:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.64,0:37:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.74,0:37:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我吧  我也这样尝试过
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.81,0:37:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是人们不会真的改变的  小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.85,0:37:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.38,0:37:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是天生与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.92,0:37:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博克岛当时面临的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.86,0:37:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是杀戮或被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.43,0:37:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我当时相信和平的希望尚存
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.67,0:37:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  你这样只会让事情更糟
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.67,0:37:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没人接受我的观点
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.61,0:38:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.51,0:38:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.31,0:38:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一条龙闯进了我们家  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.41,0:38:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摇篮里的你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.98,0:38:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我冲过去保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.02,0:38:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却看到了证明我一直以来信仰的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.04,0:38:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不是残暴的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.74,0:38:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是种聪明的  温和的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.68,0:38:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的灵魂产生了共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.02,0:38:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-瓦尔卡  快跑  -不  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.89,0:38:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.76,0:38:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  史推克
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.10,0:39:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.43,0:39:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史推克
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.07,0:39:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.81,0:39:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那晚你和你父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.08,0:39:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.68,0:39:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因为我不忍心杀死一条龙
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.68,0:39:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家族遗传啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.88,0:39:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开你们让我心碎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.95,0:39:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想只有如此你们才更安全
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.82,0:39:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么活下来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.56,0:39:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跃云并没想伤害我
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.83,0:39:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他肯定是觉得我属于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.97,0:39:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个令人炫目的野兽之家
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.04,0:39:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔法族
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.11,0:39:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世上所剩无几的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.98,0:39:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中之一了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.55,0:39:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个龙巢都有龙后
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.68,0:39:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他才是龙族之王
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.12,0:39:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可以喷出冰
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.52,0:39:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只美丽的巨兽就这样为我们建起了龙巢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.12,0:39:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个所有龙族都可以安然居住的天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.56,0:40:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  那就是喷冰龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.86,0:40:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个被摧毁的堡垒
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.73,0:40:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.90,0:40:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他保护着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.77,0:40:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们受他保护
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.10,0:40:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并听令于他
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.87,0:40:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  除了龙宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.88,0:40:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为龙宝宝谁的话也不听
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.46,0:40:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和他们住在一起二十年了  小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.53,0:40:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探索着他们的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.07,0:40:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.17,0:40:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.71,0:40:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点  吃点东西也好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.48,0:40:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.48,0:40:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为用餐时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.55,0:41:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉不好
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.62,0:41:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们早该找到小嗝嗝一起回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.76,0:41:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.93,0:41:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与他父亲同名的艾瑞特
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.15,0:41:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我的梦中情人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.80,0:41:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.20,0:41:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是宝贝  我都为你留了胡子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.67,0:41:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.60,0:41:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们被德拉戈打下来了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.10,0:41:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定他们需要我们帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.81,0:41:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得去找他们
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.57,0:41:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.61,0:41:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  史推克说
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.78,0:41:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是他们真被抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.01,0:41:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管他说过什么都不重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.21,0:41:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.58,0:41:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.69,0:41:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在无处可去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.95,0:41:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无货可卖  而且都
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.96,0:41:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性命难保了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.22,0:41:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-艾瑞特  -如果我们不快点
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.86,0:41:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到几只龙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.76,0:41:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许愿时要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.76,0:41:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-想想办法  -艾瑞特
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.53,0:41:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会想念你的  艾瑞特
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.53,0:41:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.53,0:41:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绑架你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.70,0:41:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带他飞行吗  行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.24,0:41:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.91,0:41:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带我们去找德拉戈
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.91,0:41:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后帮龙骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.58,0:41:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷溜进德拉戈的营地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.08,0:41:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是现在杀了我算了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.15,0:42:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.25,0:42:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风中飞  放开他
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.92,0:42:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.58,0:42:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.85,0:42:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风中飞  抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.89,0:42:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.99,0:42:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我带你们去找德拉戈
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.86,0:42:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百试不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.77,0:42:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是要去吃东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.28,0:42:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.84,0:43:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后  从龙之岛开始
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.02,0:43:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又发现了这些群岛
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.05,0:43:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.14,0:44:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次我身处高空
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.11,0:44:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至都感觉不到寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.98,0:44:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沉浸在...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.34,0:44:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由里
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.42,0:44:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.38,0:44:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为龙的感觉  小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.65,0:44:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全可以
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.72,0:44:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自称为龙
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.96,0:44:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你能飞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.78,0:44:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦不
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.76,0:45:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计  真是千钧一发
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.43,0:45:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这次差点就成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.03,0:45:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒极了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.30,0:45:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.25,0:45:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多年以来  你竟然这么像我
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.82,0:45:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.72,0:45:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.72,0:45:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的非常抱歉  小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.99,0:45:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们重头再来可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.13,0:45:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能再给我一次机会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.37,0:45:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我可以教你这二十年来
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.91,0:45:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我学到的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.91,0:45:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.05,0:45:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你可以做急转弯了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.22,0:46:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你能这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.49,0:46:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每种龙
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.09,0:46:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都有自己独特的秘密  而且
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.33,0:46:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把这些都教给你
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.36,0:46:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以解开所有的谜题
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.90,0:46:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到所有种族  母与子  我们俩一起
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.54,0:46:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们共同拥有的这个天赋  小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.98,0:46:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我们紧紧联系在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.98,0:46:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真实的你  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.08,0:46:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真实的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.85,0:46:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以改变龙族的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.49,0:46:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它变的更好更安全
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.29,0:46:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.89,0:46:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.34,0:46:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这简直太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.38,0:47:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以和我一起去和德拉戈谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.58,0:47:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.05,0:47:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟德拉戈没什么好谈的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.38,0:47:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但我们得  -不行
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.89,0:47:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须保护我们的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.15,0:47:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.26,0:47:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.50,0:47:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我已经把你们带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.87,0:47:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把这家伙弄走
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.21,0:47:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远不要和龙抢玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.01,0:47:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.98,0:47:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么倒霉的总是我
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.90,0:47:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那下面是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.23,0:47:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吐出的水泡直径很大
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.50,0:47:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明肺部巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.27,0:47:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居住在深海冰水里  我想
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.51,0:48:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是五级巨兽
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.51,0:48:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许有六级
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.99,0:48:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉球  你怎么了  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.92,0:48:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钩牙  振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.81,0:48:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.91,0:48:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德拉戈
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.08,0:48:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.29,0:48:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到你总是很高兴  我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.49,0:48:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这儿取暖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.16,0:48:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你所见  我可是准时
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.70,0:48:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带了一批新龙过来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.63,0:49:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我保证的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.03,0:49:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要醒过来了  拉住他
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.63,0:49:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来人支援一下
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.20,0:49:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.70,0:49:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.20,0:49:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钩牙
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.07,0:49:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.41,0:49:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如今属于我了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.35,0:49:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外作为额外赠送的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.52,0:49:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还把他们的骑手给你抓来了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.12,0:49:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不另外收费哦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.32,0:49:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  你在开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.56,0:49:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你之前真是太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.66,0:50:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我后来发现  有好大一群龙骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.19,0:50:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们攻击了...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.03,0:50:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.70,0:50:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来德拉戈没抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.40,0:50:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有多少  -上百个
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.73,0:50:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有满满一岛的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.34,0:50:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是不担心
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.37,0:50:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话这会儿我的人就在追捕他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.64,0:50:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不会发现你的藏身之处的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.34,0:50:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.78,0:50:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会发现的  他们知道我们失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.05,0:50:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他们有会追踪的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.12,0:50:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你敢碰我们  小嗝嗝会狠狠揍...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.62,0:50:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-小嗝嗝  -他不会坏你的事儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.59,0:50:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.65,0:50:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是伟岸的史推克之子
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.06,0:50:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是博克岛首领的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.06,0:50:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是有史以来最棒的驯龙大师
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.56,0:50:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驯龙大师
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.60,0:50:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是唯一一个能控制龙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.27,0:50:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-并不是呢  -不好意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.00,0:50:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你放我们走  马上就放
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.40,0:50:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然他将会骑着他的夜煞袭卷这里
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.63,0:50:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把你的整支船队
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.87,0:50:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卷成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.21,0:50:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他们会像小宝宝一样哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.78,0:50:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是幽默风趣
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.70,0:50:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得好  宝贝儿
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.58,0:51:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  像小宝宝一样哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.25,0:51:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们总是哭个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.58,0:51:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是群小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.49,0:51:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起先  你说只有一个龙骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.82,0:51:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在整个博克岛都是了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.49,0:51:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你还带着他们找上门来了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.40,0:51:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德拉戈
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.17,0:51:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下一切准备工作
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.17,0:51:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须得马上出击龙骑士的老巢
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.21,0:51:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要干掉他们龙王
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.58,0:51:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后占领整个博克岛
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.71,0:51:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德拉戈
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.32,0:51:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.52,0:51:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德拉戈  拜托  我...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.13,0:51:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风中飞
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.40,0:51:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.18,0:52:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.31,0:52:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能等着德拉戈来攻击这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.42,0:52:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得先一步找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.53,0:52:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.80,0:52:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡定
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.50,0:52:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你开什么玩笑  你是怎么进来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.57,0:52:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么进来就怎么出去
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.13,0:52:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们  -安全
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.84,0:52:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没牙仔  跟上  -等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.74,0:52:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  爸  有...有件事你得知道
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.47,0:52:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行  行  路上再说
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.54,0:52:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是什么可以"路上再说"的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.54,0:52:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再听了  小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.75,0:52:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有更多惊天动地的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.41,0:52:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事件发展和变化
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.58,0:52:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊  又一件
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.22,0:52:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.82,0:52:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸  和其他大部分我告诉你的"惊喜"不同
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.19,0:52:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证你会喜欢这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.49,0:52:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过你需要小心消化一下
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.53,0:52:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.36,0:52:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你会想自己处理一下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.53,0:52:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.33,0:52:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.25,0:53:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  能请您把剑放下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.89,0:53:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你想要说什么  史推克
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.66,0:53:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么能那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.39,0:53:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些年来一直躲在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.43,0:53:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有为什么我没有回到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.50,0:53:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到儿子身边
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.73,0:53:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了任何你可能会改变的希望吗  史推克
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.41,0:53:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是博克岛的人可能会改变的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.44,0:53:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我祈求了这么多次
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.71,0:53:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你们停止战争  去寻找其他解决方法
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.71,0:53:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你们有人听过我的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.51,0:53:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我不结婚的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.98,0:53:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一个原因  还有另一个
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.18,0:53:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我留你独自一个人抚养小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.59,0:53:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想着没有我在身边  他会更好
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.63,0:53:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.23,0:53:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今我看清了这一点  但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.40,0:54:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么一言不发的  史推克
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.27,0:54:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.48,0:54:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大吼  大叫  说点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.74,0:54:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是和我失去你的那天一般美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.68,0:54:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一天还能更糟糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.86,0:54:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.02,0:54:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就要跳进冰冷的水里
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.64,0:54:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后被淹死了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.05,0:54:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来真凉爽
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.75,0:54:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧  女士优先
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.34,0:55:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是一坨龙大便
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.39,0:55:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹲下
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.93,0:55:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去警告其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.87,0:55:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住他们  艾瑞特
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.37,0:55:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.84,0:55:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我再次爱上了你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.38,0:55:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可悲呀
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.42,0:55:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还可以去跳海
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.65,0:55:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还要不要去救出你们的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.68,0:55:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后逃离这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.05,0:55:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,检查每一个捕龙夹
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.95,0:55:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就在这儿的某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.86,0:55:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉球
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.70,0:55:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人往这边来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.64,0:55:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  你继续做手头上的事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.70,0:55:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续转
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.72,0:56:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你救了我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.13,0:56:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在让我还你一个人情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.87,0:56:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  你绝对会认不出来那个地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.84,0:56:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去我们造武器的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.04,0:56:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今用来造龙鞍
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.14,0:56:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翅蹬
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.68,0:56:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们...我们甚至还给龙补牙
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.64,0:56:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会相信一切的变化是有多大
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.08,0:56:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀  你儿子把博克岛变得更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.38,0:56:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这件事上我们做得不错  瓦尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.45,0:56:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.72,0:56:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.45,0:56:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.80,0:56:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.44,0:56:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点生疏了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.80,0:56:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.67,0:56:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是因为你的厨艺才娶你的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.40,0:56:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望不是
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.34,0:56:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她做的肉丸  杀伤力比一把战斧都大
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.68,0:57:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的肚子对她的肉丸可一直印象深刻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.53,0:57:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你带着你所有的龙一起回来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.98,0:57:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老德拉戈根本毫无胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.45,0:57:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都会顺顺利利的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.41,0:57:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢点  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.35,0:57:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多需要考虑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.58,0:57:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.80,0:57:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱死这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.82,0:57:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得我们的歌吗  瓦尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.19,0:57:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将畅游航行在茫茫大海中
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.74,0:57:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不曾畏惧巨浪淹没我
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.74,0:58:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢乐地驾驭着生活的波涛
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.54,0:58:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你愿嫁给我
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.24,0:58:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论炙热的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.81,0:58:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是刺骨的寒凉
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.90,0:58:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不会...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.58,0:58:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不会阻挡我的...步...伐...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.09,0:58:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.60,0:58:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你许我你的芳心
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.00,0:58:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且爱...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.66,0:58:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且爱我永不停
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.96,0:58:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最亲爱的我的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.11,0:59:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你话语掷地有声震撼我
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.40,0:59:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我并不需要这些海誓山盟
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.71,0:59:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你的臂弯环绕我
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.86,0:59:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我愿送你金戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.52,0:59:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也愿为你吟歌唱诗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.00,0:59:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.56,0:59:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会护你远离一切灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.65,0:59:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你愿待在我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.99,0:59:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金戒指对我没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.29,0:59:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不欣赏你的诗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.64,0:59:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只希望能牵着你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.07,0:59:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只希望你在我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.31,0:59:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱你  吻你  紧拥你
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.61,0:59:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与你共舞  共入梦乡
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.78,0:59:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起走过风风雨雨
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.54,0:59:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将把你的笑容珍藏在身侧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.49,0:59:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将畅游航行在茫茫大海中
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.24,0:59:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不曾畏惧巨浪淹没我
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.11,0:59:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢乐地驾驭着生活的波涛
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.77,0:59:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你愿嫁给我
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.12,0:59:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我还在坚持唱哦...  -戈伯
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.91,0:59:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唱完了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.28,0:59:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为至死也不能与你共舞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.29,0:59:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要给我下猛药啦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.76,0:59:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了你  我亲爱的...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.09,1:00:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意做任何事
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.93,1:00:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意回家吗  瓦尔卡
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.23,1:00:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意重新成为我的妻子吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.97,1:00:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以重组一个家庭
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.71,1:00:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.85,1:00:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.25,1:00:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了  以后做饭我来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.25,1:00:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢奥丁神你没听我的话  儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.72,1:00:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我们永远都找不到对方了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.93,1:00:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没牙仔
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.07,1:00:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.89,1:01:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.06,1:01:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔卡...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.66,1:01:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔卡  没事的  没事的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.66,1:01:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在是一个团队了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.06,1:01:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  你想怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.33,1:01:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得拯救那些龙
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.97,1:01:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  没问题
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.60,1:01:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.71,1:01:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装弹
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.34,1:01:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.78,1:01:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火  开火
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.22,1:01:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管任何代价  坚持进攻那座山
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.19,1:01:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得把龙王引出来
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.40,1:01:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好捕龙夹
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.49,1:02:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊喜
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.76,1:02:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.26,1:02:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.03,1:02:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上还真是惊喜连连呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.33,1:02:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.94,1:02:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙骑士驾到
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.01,1:02:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喷火
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.98,1:02:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.42,1:02:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们砍下来
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.26,1:02:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和父亲同名的艾瑞特
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.20,1:03:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往上飞  姑娘
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.77,1:03:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向左倾斜  艾瑞特
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.01,1:03:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.14,1:03:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.25,1:03:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶  宝贝儿
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.36,1:03:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.53,1:03:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当心哦[双关为"抬头"]
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.37,1:03:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驯龙大师
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.47,1:03:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎加入  龙骑士
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.21,1:03:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得说  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.84,1:03:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.44,1:03:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和妈妈叙叙旧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.19,1:03:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.93,1:03:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你知道我的表演天赋是从哪来的了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.23,1:04:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙王
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.87,1:04:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有场硬仗要打了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.22,1:04:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  没牙仔
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.49,1:04:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们瞧瞧你的厉害  伙计
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.23,1:04:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.61,1:04:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一刻我等了许久了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.14,1:04:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法夺走我们的龙
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.51,1:04:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是由龙王控制的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.25,1:04:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好我带来了一位挑战者
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.21,1:05:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一只龙王
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.51,1:05:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是只十级的龙  十级的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.01,1:05:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.68,1:05:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不...不要...  -来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.39,1:05:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉那只龙王
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.42,1:05:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.20,1:05:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.97,1:05:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了你  我亲爱的...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.67,1:05:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意做任何事
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.05,1:05:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔卡  你觉得你能阻止他们吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.18,1:06:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽力的  来吧  跃云
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.62,1:06:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.62,1:06:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看着你被烧着了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.99,1:06:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想杀我这点火还不够
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.08,1:06:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史推克
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.77,1:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.24,1:06:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.06,1:07:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赢了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.47,1:07:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.80,1:07:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉她
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.54,1:07:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.11,1:07:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持住
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.28,1:07:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲啊  裂颅
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.58,1:07:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟上  戈伯
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.72,1:07:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧紧跟在你后面呢  史推克
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.20,1:08:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.57,1:08:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.68,1:08:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...就是所谓的驯龙大师吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.72,1:08:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟岸的史推克之子吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.72,1:08:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他该感到多羞愧啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.56,1:08:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有这些伤害...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.30,1:08:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都为了些什么
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.83,1:08:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了变得无人能敌吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.80,1:08:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了统治世界吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.24,1:08:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙  他们...他们是善良的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.96,1:08:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神奇的生物  能与人类和平相处
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.74,1:08:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者伤害人类
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.91,1:08:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞧  我知道生活在恐惧中是什么滋味
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.92,1:08:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道自己的村庄被焚毁
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.59,1:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家庭被毁灭是什么滋味
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.63,1:08:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是即便小时候
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.36,1:08:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无依无靠
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.56,1:09:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也发誓要
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.73,1:09:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战胜对龙的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.77,1:09:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且解放这世上所有的人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.14,1:09:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么要组建龙族军队
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.44,1:09:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要用龙来战胜其它龙
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.85,1:09:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又或者你是要用龙来征服人类
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.25,1:09:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来控制追随你的人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.15,1:09:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消灭违抗你的人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.22,1:09:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聪明
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.49,1:09:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界需要和平
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.93,1:09:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博克岛已经找到了人龙和平共处的方式
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.27,1:09:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我展示给你看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.40,1:09:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.47,1:09:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是让我
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.24,1:09:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展示给你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.92,1:09:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.72,1:09:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.89,1:10:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来  戈伯
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.36,1:10:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  计划有变
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.90,1:10:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何龙都无法违抗龙王的命令
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.63,1:10:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以谁控制了龙王
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.67,1:10:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就控制了所有龙
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.44,1:10:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没牙仔
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.22,1:10:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没牙仔  你没事吧  伙计  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.59,1:10:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你见识一下真正的厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.59,1:10:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制其它龙的强大意念力
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.50,1:10:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与之相比
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.23,1:10:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你微不足道
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.71,1:10:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他刚刚跟你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.25,1:10:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没牙仔  拜托
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.75,1:10:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.55,1:11:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  不  拜托  你这是干吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.35,1:11:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.75,1:11:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停  快醒过来
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.70,1:11:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没牙仔  不要
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.53,1:11:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没牙仔
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.40,1:11:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不要  -小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.37,1:11:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-住手  -儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.51,1:11:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.51,1:11:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.76,1:11:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.97,1:11:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.64,1:11:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史推克
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.81,1:12:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.38,1:12:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.00,1:12:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.71,1:12:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  不  不
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.86,1:12:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  别碰他
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.00,1:12:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走  走开
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.64,1:13:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走开
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.47,1:13:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是他的错
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.44,1:13:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你心里清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.65,1:13:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驯良的龙
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.72,1:13:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在坏人的控制下
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.59,1:13:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  等等  别走  -也会做坏事
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.91,1:13:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.58,1:13:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集所有人在博克岛会合
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.91,1:13:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没牙仔  -不  别去
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.81,1:14:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿武神迎接你
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.55,1:14:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引领你穿过奥丁的伟大战场
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.58,1:14:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿他们用爱和狂怒歌唱你的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.85,1:14:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们听到由瓦尔哈拉殿堂深处传来的颂歌
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.85,1:14:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}北欧神话主神兼死亡之神奥丁接待英灵的殿堂
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.82,1:14:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在国王之桌上
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.69,1:14:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已获得了应有的席位
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.60,1:14:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位伟人从此陨落
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.87,1:14:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他同时也是一名勇士
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.60,1:14:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位族长
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.60,1:14:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位慈父
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.61,1:14:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一位挚友
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.24,1:15:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  爸
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.79,1:15:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没能成为
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.06,1:15:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你期望中的领袖
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.23,1:15:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没能像我想象中那样捍卫和平
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.90,1:15:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.18,1:16:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个早产儿
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.18,1:16:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出生的时候个子好小
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.82,1:16:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那么脆弱  那么不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.32,1:16:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕你会夭折
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.69,1:16:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.26,1:16:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从未怀疑过
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.07,1:16:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他总说你会成为他们之中最强壮的一个
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.34,1:16:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说对了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.87,1:16:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拥有领袖的心胸
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.81,1:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和龙的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.25,1:16:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你才能把我们的世界维系起来
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.99,1:16:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是这样的人  儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.60,1:16:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.97,1:16:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾好怕变成父亲那样
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.38,1:17:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我觉得我将永远无法做到像他那样
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.05,1:17:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酒精怎么才能成为一个
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.12,1:17:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么伟大  那么勇敢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.72,1:17:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么无私的人呢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.32,1:17:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我只有尽力了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.70,1:17:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首领要保卫自己的领土
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.67,1:17:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要回去
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.98,1:17:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么回  -他把所有龙都带走了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.98,1:17:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是所有龙
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.09,1:17:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.40,1:17:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们根本没办法控制这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.67,1:17:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.30,1:18:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是那只龙王
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.04,1:18:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会也把这些小家伙给控制了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.81,1:18:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是龙宝宝  才不会听任何人的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.71,1:18:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  就像我们一样
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.85,1:18:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这实在是  太危险了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.05,1:18:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人可能会说
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.42,1:18:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这主意糟透了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.02,1:18:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好我从不听话
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.46,1:18:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.90,1:18:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有什么
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.90,1:18:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.26,1:18:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺回没牙仔  狠狠教训德拉戈
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.23,1:18:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.07,1:18:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这件事
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.43,1:18:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.17,1:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  看着点家具
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.10,1:19:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.79,1:19:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的首领已经死了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.83,1:19:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-史推克  -不  不可能
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.20,1:19:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没人能保护你们了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.08,1:19:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.48,1:19:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他带走了所有龙
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.29,1:19:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引开龙王
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.92,1:19:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他无暇顾及没牙仔
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.39,1:19:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么引开他啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.89,1:20:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你忘了你的战斗伙伴是谁了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.06,1:20:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有我驯服不了的龙
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.50,1:20:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这只除外  -半吊子
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.57,1:20:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊  是小嗝嗝
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.57,1:20:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.96,1:20:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续扔羊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.59,1:20:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑羊来了  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.60,1:20:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.62,1:21:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.10,1:21:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我承认  想甩掉你还真不容易
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.50,1:21:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没牙仔
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.50,1:21:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  伙计
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.61,1:21:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.11,1:21:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  我在这呢  伙计
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.18,1:21:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回我这来
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.01,1:21:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经不是你的了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.65,1:21:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在属于龙王
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.05,1:21:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  请便吧  驯龙大师
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.52,1:21:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以试试
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.16,1:21:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他第二次可不会失手了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.59,1:21:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是你的错  伙计
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.30,1:21:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们逼你做的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.18,1:22:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永远也不会伤害他的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.25,1:22:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永远也不会伤害我的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.69,1:22:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.66,1:22:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你了  你是我最好的朋友  伙计
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.30,1:22:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.04,1:22:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的  这就对啦
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.44,1:22:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在这儿
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.48,1:22:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.02,1:22:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持住
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.59,1:22:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快够到你了  伙计  我这就来了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.57,1:22:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想办法啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.07,1:23:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得把他们俩分开
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.28,1:23:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须屏蔽掉控制  没牙仔
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.75,1:23:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你信任我吗  伙计
